        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "To eliminate the 4 in the second row using the 1 in the first row: $R_2 - 4R_1$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Find the inverse of $\\begin{bmatrix} 5 & 2 \\\\ 2 & 1 \\end{bmatrix}$.",
        "options": ["$\\begin{bmatrix} 1 & -2 \\\\ -2 & 5 \\end{bmatrix}$", "$\\begin{bmatrix} -1 & 2 \\\\ 2 & -5 \\end{bmatrix}$", "$\\begin{bmatrix} 5 & -2 \\\\ -2 & 1 \\end{bmatrix}$", "$\\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 2 \\\\ 2 & 5 \\end{bmatrix}$"],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$\\det = 5-4 = 1$. Swap 5 and 1, negate the 2s."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Evaluate the determinant of $\\begin{bmatrix} 2 & -1 & 0 \\\\ 3 & 2 & 1 \\\\ 0 & 1 & 4 \\end{bmatrix}$.",
