        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$0.5(2r)^2(0.5\\theta) = 0.5(4r^2)(0.5\\theta) = 2(0.5r^2\\theta)$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Find the reference angle of $17\\pi/6$.",
