        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "Coterminal with $5\\pi/6$ (Quadrant II). $\\pi - 5\\pi/6 = \\pi/6$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "In a right triangle, if $\\cos \\theta = 0.8$, find $\\csc \\theta$.",
