        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$\\cos = 4/5 \\implies \\sin = 3/5 \\implies \\csc = 5/3$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Simplify $\\frac{\\cos^2 \\theta}{1 - \\sin \\theta}$.",
