        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$(1 - \\sin^2 \\theta)/(1 - \\sin \\theta) = (1-\\sin\\theta)(1+\\sin\\theta)/(1-\\sin\\theta) = 1 + \\sin \\theta$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "A 6ft tall man casts a 4ft shadow. Find the tangent of the angle of elevation of the sun.",
