        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$0.4 + 0.5 - (0.4 \\cdot 0.5) = 0.9 - 0.2 = 0.7$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Find the vertex of the parabola $x^2 - 4x - 4y = 0$.",
